                  <h2 class="content-h2" style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.25;">The 12-month implementation pitch is dead.<br>Here's what replaced it.</h2>
                  <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#C8392A;letter-spacing:0.5px;text-transform:uppercase;">Building a 90-day proof case</p>

                  <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#444444;">
                    Buyers have zero patience for "trust us, it'll pay off." The companies winning right now build 90-day proof cases with hard dollar metrics before asking for the real budget. They run structured pilots that generate CFO-ready numbers, then use those numbers to unlock the full contract.
                  </p>

                  <!-- Jacob Reese quote -->
                  <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin:0 0 24px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background-color:#fdf6f5;border-radius:6px;padding:24px 24px 20px;border-top:2px solid #C8392A;">
                        <p style="margin:0 0 14px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:#1a1a1a;font-style:italic;">
                          "Our biggest tech misstep in 2025 was rolling out a new VMI inventory tracking system across 15 customer locations without proper pilot testing. We pushed it live to hit Q1 goals, and within three weeks our restocking accuracy dropped from 94% to 71%. We'd spent six figures on tech that made us worse at the exact thing that differentiated us. For 2026, we completely changed our approach. Now we pilot any system at just 2-3 locations for a full quarter, and our veteran team members have veto power if the tech doesn't match real-world job site conditions."
                        </p>
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td>
                              <p style="margin:0 0 1px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#1a1a1a;">Jacob Reese</p>
                              <p style="margin:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#888888;">VP, Standard Plumbing &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="https://techronicler.com/the-glitch-report-what-went-wrong-in-tech-in-2025-and-how-we-fixed-it/@TrackLink" style="color:#C8392A;text-decoration:none;">via TechRonicler</a></p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- Stat grid -->
                  <table class="stat-block" role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin:24px 0;">
                    <tr>
                      <td width="50%" style="padding:0 8px 0 0;vertical-align:top;">
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="background-color:#fdf6f5;border-radius:6px;padding:16px;border-top:2px solid #C8392A;">
                              <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#C8392A;line-height:1;">57%</p>
                              <p style="margin:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#555555;">of B2B buyers now expect ROI within 3 months of purchase</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                      <td width="50%" style="padding:0 0 0 8px;vertical-align:top;">
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="background-color:#fdf6f5;border-radius:6px;padding:16px;border-top:2px solid #C8392A;">
                              <p style="margin:0 0 4px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#C8392A;line-height:1;">72%</p>
                              <p style="margin:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;color:#555555;">more likely to sign a full contract after a successful pilot</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr><td colspan="2" style="height:12px;">&nbsp;</td></tr>
                    <tr>
                      <td width="50%" style="padding:0 8px 0 0;vertical-align:top;">
                        <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                          <tr>
